data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of modern design and comfort. The open floor plan and vaulted ceiling create an airy and inviting atmosphere, making the space feel expansive and connected.. Step into the living room and immediately notice the seamless flow into the adjacent office space. Adorned with French doors, this room presents a versatile opportunity – whether it's a home office or an additional bedroom for guests. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a kitchen island, and granite countertops. Retreat to the primary bedroom, complete with an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Step outside into the fenced backyard, an oasis of relaxation and entertainment. The covered patio is the perfect spot to unwind or host a barbecue. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a viewing today!
